Package ca.corefacility.gview.map.items

Provides for implementations of specific items to be displayed on the GView map.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BackboneItem
    An item which has a particular location on the backbone.
    BackboneShapeItem
    Describes a shape which is bound to the backbone.
    BackboneTextItem
    Describes a Text item that is to be pinned to the backbone.
    FeatureItem  
    MapComponent
    Defines something that can go onto a map.
    MapItem
    An item that is stored on a map.
    ShapeItem
    Describes an item on the map which has a shape.
    TextItem
    Describes an item which consists of text.
